_sText: This is the map de_greensleeves. ------------------------------------------------------------------------ Terrorists have been using an abandoned castle to secretly manufacture alcohol and narcotics to sell to the public. Police have become aware of this illegal activity and plan to move in using a crack force of the worlds best poilce teams. The terrorists discover the police's plan and have no option but to try and blow up all the evidence left by their scheme. ------------------------------------------------------------------------ The map has been in developement for close to 2 years and i finally feel its finished enough to release. Its been a project that i have started and stopped many times and it has frustrated me hugely at times, so its a huge relief to finally get it out there and for people to enjoy. -The map has 64 spawnpoints but i recommend up to 32. -It has colorcorrection and hdr so make sure those options are turned on in your graphics settings. -The map has a rather large easter egg, with a custom song made for me by my very good friend Sam 'kulture' Dickison. check out his music here: www.myspace.com/kulture_uk So a big thanks to him for taking the time to add a little GMT. Also want to say a big thanks to Nath and all those who encouraged and played/ commented on the map as it was made. Wouldnt be in this state without you guys so thanks. ----------------------------------------------------------------------- Lastly thanks to anyone who presses the download button; ive spent a lot of time and energy making this so you are the guys who make it worth it. If anyone adds this to a servers rotation or wants me to tell them where the easter egg is PM me. Thanks again.
